string 2:
Let's throw down sometime. I love a fair match! What kind of
competitions do you like?

I love those, too! They're a test not only of speed, but of
courage!
I see. You want to make it a battle of the minds, then!

So not you versus me, but us against a puzzling mystery?
Sounds like a ton of fun!
I don't wanna compete with you.

It's a match, not a fight... Still, I appreciate the thought. We'll
always be pals!
How does my pitch-black form look to you?

That is upsetting, but I appreciate your candor. Such frankness
is worthy of trust.

Merely the Black Digitron's effect, but it ups my power, and I
like its look as well.
Makes you look like some evil mastermind.

I am hardly the manipulative type! I would not mind offering
you my guidance, however.

Do not judge by looks aloneâ€”though I did ask. For the sake
of our bond, I will forgive you.
